Package com.intel.hadoop.graphbuilder.parser

Interface Summary
FieldParser<ValueType> Parser for a specific data type.
GraphParser<VidType extends WritableComparable<VidType>,VertexData extends Writable,EdgeData extends Writable> A interface for parsing vertices and edges of a graph.
 

Class Summary

FloatParser Parser for FloatType.

LongParser Parser for LongType
